## tacc-keys list

List all public ssh keys registered to a user

### Synopsis

List all public ssh keys registered to a user. The keys will be printed
using the following format:
    
    key-id:int tag:string
    ssh-pubkey:string

```
tacc-keys list [username] [flags]
```
